OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777554668
OL,3,CPolice patrols increased to support
OL,4,CJewish communities across the Thames
OL,5,CValley
OL,7,FPolice patrols across the Thames
OL,8,FValley are being increased following a
OL,9,Fterrorist incident in north London
OL,10,Fyesterday where two Jewish men were
OL,11,Fstabbed.
OL,13,FA 45-year-old man, said by police to
OL,14,Fbe a Somali-born British national, was
OL,15,Farrested following the incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
