FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777554668
OL,3,CPolice patrols increased to support
OL,4,CJewish communities across the Thames
OL,5,CValley
OL,7,FThe stabbings are the latest in a
OL,8,Fseries of attacks on Jewish sites over
OL,9,Frecent weeks and have prompted calls
OL,10,Ffor urgent action and accusations the
OL,11,FGovernment has not done enough to
OL,12,Ftackle antisemitism.
OL,14,FFollowing the incident, Thames Valley
OL,15,FPolice Assistant Chief Constable
OL,16,FChristian Bunt said:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777554668
OL,3,CPolice patrols increased to support
OL,4,CJewish communities across the Thames
OL,5,CValley
OL,7,F"We are aware of the terrorist attack
OL,8,Fin Golders Green, North London, today.
OL,9,FAs a result, we will be increasing our
OL,10,Fpatrols to provide reassurance and
OL,11,Fsupport to our Jewish communities
OL,12,Fwithin the Thames Valley.
OL,14,F"Our Jewish communities and the wider
OL,15,Fpublic can expect to see an enhanced
OL,16,Fpolicing presence around key
OL,17,Flocations, including places of
OL,18,Fworship. This will include armed
OL,19,Fresponse vehicles and is standard
OL,20,Fpractice in response to terrorist
OL,21,Fincidents such as this one.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777554668
OL,3,CPolice patrols increased to support
OL,4,CJewish communities across the Thames
OL,5,CValley
OL,7,F"Please do speak to our officers out
OL,8,Fand about if you have any questions,
OL,9,Fconcerns or information to share. We
OL,10,Fare asking the public to please remain
OL,11,Fvigilant and report anything that
OL,12,Fdoesn't feel right to police via the
OL,13,FAnti-Terrorist Hotline on 0800 789
OL,14,F123, information that you share can
OL,15,Fmake a difference. Always call 999 in
OL,16,Fan emergency.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
