OL,3,CPolice patrols increased to support
OL,4,CJewish communities across the Thames
OL,5,CValley
OL,7,FHe is also expected to meet criminal
OL,8,Fjustice agencies on Thursday to
OL,9,Fdiscuss the attack, and said he would
OL,10,Fvisit Golders Green "as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible".
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
